subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: This complex development programme is aimed at joint, coordinated and targeted action to improve human resources development; to enhance the social capital, self-help and community support, public services and local community initiatives; to create and mobilize the internal resources of the local economy; and to improve accessibility of the settlements and access of the population to services, thus helping the social integration of this region.
subproject.title: HUN Cserehat Programme
